Package: m6ACalibrateR
Type: Package
Title: A Machine Learning-Based Calibration Method for Enhanced Accuracy and Consistency in m6A Epitranscriptome Mapping
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Haokai", "Ye", email = "haokai.ye17@student.xjtlu.edu.cn",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Haokai Ye <haokai.ye17@student.xjtlu.edu.cn>
Description: m6ACalibrateR addresses the discrepancies in m6A maps across studies by calibrating transcriptome-wide m6A maps.
  The package integrates genomic features to identify and eliminate non-specific antibody enrichment-induced false positives in MeRIP-seq, 
  generating a high-accuracy m6A epitranscriptome map.
